2011-03-18  Christopher M. Fuhrman

      * :Fine::_fatal() will croak if called directly
        
        Log::Fine::_fatal() will croak if called directly as it is not
        {no_croak} aware.  Add CAVEAT section to Log::Fine::Utils documenting
        this
